      "patchset_number": 6,
      "line": 251,
      "message": "I think all we need here is to add [ and ] to:\nCharMatcher.anyOf(\"\\\"\\'\") \ni.e. :\nCharMatcher.anyOf(\"\\\"\\'[]\") \n\nI dont see the reason to drop the single quote from the matcher, or the reason to replace trim() with removeFrom()",
