      "message": "The string part of { $juel: [ \"Hi, ${arg[0]}\", { get_input: name } ] } is:\n\"Hi, ${arg[0]}\"\nit will be trimmed to:\nHi, ${arg[0]}\nI am not seeing any issue with this in testing\n\nIf I remember correctly the single quote was also removed as it was causing issues",
